Text:
Thanks for sharing all these great DCP packs over the years, DarkElf.

Now that it's been announced that TPB is switching to a paid model, do you have an idea of where you'll be uploading instead? I'm sure that your fans would like know where we should go in the future for our comic fix.

Thanks Darkelf. Always the highlight of my week.

And the same question as drdoombot, any idea where you'll be uploading to after the changes?
Thanks Darkelf...  ditto I'd follow if I knew where you were going, if you are going??
Thanks for the years of service DE.  I'd also like to know where you're heading, these packs of yours turned me on to some good comics I never would have bought otherwise.
love to see you on torrrentleech DarkElf.  thanks for all your ups.
Thanks so much Darkelf!  You are the man.
I'm the same as above, if you stay, I stay. If you go, I go.
